===Interjection===
{{en-intj|pos=[[God]] [[bless]] [[you]]!}}

# {{non-gloss definition|Short for '''May God [[bless you]]'''; said as a short prayer for the recipient.}}
# {{non-gloss definition|Said to somebody who has [[sneeze]]d, as a rhetorical response.}} (see also [[bless you]])

